---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString();
---

<Layout
  metadata={{
    title: 'Privacy Policy',
    description: 'How TapRebook collects, uses, and protects your data.',
  }}
>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </section>

  <section class="prose prose-invert max-w-4xl">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>TapRebook helps organizations manage operational messaging on WhatsApp. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have.</p>

    <h2>Data we process</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account &amp; billing</strong>: name, email, organization details.</li>
      <li><strong>Operational messages</strong>: message metadata, template IDs, delivery events, tags.</li>
      <li><strong>Integrations</strong>: identifiers/keys required to connect tools (e.g., WhatsApp BSP, Google Sheets).</li>
      <li><strong>Product analytics</strong>: basic usage events to improve reliability and UX.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Provide and secure the service</li>
      <li>Operate automated flows per your settings</li>
      <li>Measure completion, drop-off, and exceptions</li>
      <li>Support, troubleshooting, and legal compliance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>We retain operational records only as long as needed to deliver the service and meet legal obligations. You may request deletion where applicable.</p>

    <h2>International transfers</h2>
    <p>Data may be processed in jurisdictions where we or our service providers operate, with appropriate safeguards in place.</p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>Subject to local law, you may access, correct, export, or delete your personal data. Contact us at <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>.</p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>See our <a href="/security/">Application &amp; Data Security</a> page for technical and organizational measures.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy inquiries, email <a href="mailto:privacy@taprebook.com">privacy@taprebook.com</a>.</p>

    <p class="text-xs opacity-80 mt-8">This page is provided for informational purposes and does not constitute legal advice.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

